radiation and the width of the prohibited zone were also 
studied. Single USP of the fundamental and second harmonics of 
YAlO[.sup]3[/]:Nd laser with a passive synchronization of the 
modes were used as the excitation source and for probing. The 
USP duration was about 15 ps. 
